Here is a CSS script to make your topnav button nice and responsive with smooth transitions.

CSS
.topnav {
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #985e4e;
  }

  .topnav a {
    float: left;
    color: #f2f2f2;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 17px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: border-radius 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .topnav a:hover {
    background-color: #ddd;
    color: black;
    border-radius: 0%;
  }
